Bunny Rescue is an exciting, highly captivating game. The goal of this game is to help the cute bunny make his through the different strange levels and try to escape the tunnel. Can you really him make it out alive?

Bunny Rescue is a simple yet addictive gameplay. Help the bunny to reach the tunnel by letting them jump and cross the edge of it. Use your mind power and speed to make it out if the tunnel. Good Luck!

+++ GAME FEATURES +++
Easy to learn game play
Catchy music
Great graphics
Funny character
